content: Marketing Strategy Presentation: Our 2025 marketing strategy focuses on digital channels and customer engagement. Key initiatives include social media campaigns, content marketing, and influencer partnerships. Target demographics are millennials and Gen Z consumers aged 25-40. Budget allocation: 40% digital advertising, 30% content creation, 20% events, 10% traditional media. Expected ROI is 3.5x within 12 months.
